
= SDL_SemValue =
Use this function to get the current value of a semaphore.


== Syntax ==
<syntaxhighlight lang='c++'>
Uint32 SDL_SemValue(SDL_sem* sem)
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''sem'''
|the semaphore to query
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns the current value of the semaphore.

